Uses of Interface
net.bytebuddy.implementation.attribute.AnnotationAppender

  • Packages that use AnnotationAppender 
    Package Description
    net.bytebuddy.implementation.attribute
    All types and classes in this package are responsible for writing attributes for a given Java byte code element, i.e. fields, types and byte code methods.

    • Uses of AnnotationAppender in net.bytebuddy.implementation.attribute

      static class  AnnotationAppender.Default
      A default implementation for an annotation appender that writes annotations to a given byte consumer represented by an ASM AnnotationVisitor.
